[[File:Dani12.jpg|thumb|right|90px|Dani is subjected to the [[Torture/Legends|tortures]] of the analysis grid.]] {{Quote|The analysis is as painful as it looks...though the body does survive it. Unless the stress destroys the mind, in which case...|[[Den Siva]]|<ref name="Star Wars (1977) 97">[[Star Wars (1977) 97|''Star Wars'' (1977) 97]]</ref>}}
The '''analysis grid''' was a device that fired coherent beams of energy through a specimen, revealing much about them. The analysis was an extremely painful process for the specimen, as the energy beams used the same technology as blasters. [[Den Siva]] made use of an analysis grid to examine the [[Zeltron/Legends|Zeltron]] [[Dani/Legends|Dani]] on [[Kinooine/Legends|Kinooine]].<ref name="Star Wars (1977) 97" />

